  "datePublished": "2026-04-07",
  "description": "The obligation on the owner of a plan to ensure it converges toward its goal — maintaining tasks, tracking dependencies, surfacing blockers, and reporting progress. Distinct from the duty of execution: the steward ensures the work gets done, not that any specific task is performed.",
  "name": "Duty of Plan Stewardship",
